OL,3,CGovernment urged to help amid warning
OL,4,Cmanufacturing sector has 'hit the
OL,5,Cbuffers'
OL,7,FThe Government is being urged to help
OL,8,Fmanufacturers after a new report
OL,9,Fwarned the sector has "hit the
OL,10,Fbuffers".
OL,12,FMake UK and business advisers BDO said
OL,13,Ftheir research among more than 300
OL,14,Fmanufacturers suggested that
OL,15,Fincreasing employment taxes and wider
OL,16,Fbusiness costs were affecting
OL,17,Fcompanies, as well as worries of a
OL,18,Fglobal trade war.
