OL,3,CGovernment urged to help amid warning
OL,4,Cmanufacturing sector has 'hit the
OL,5,Cbuffers'
OL,7,FFirms are freezing recruitment and
OL,8,Fconsidering redundancies, while
OL,9,Finvestment plans are being delayed and
OL,10,Fin some cases cancelled altogether,
OL,11,Fsaid the report.
OL,13,FMake UK called on the Government to
OL,14,Freform business rates, fix the
OL,15,F"broken" skills system and launch a
OL,16,Flong-term industrial strategy which
OL,17,Fhas advanced manufacturing at its
OL,18,Fheart.
