OL,3,CGovernment urged to help amid warning
OL,4,Cmanufacturing sector has 'hit the
OL,5,Cbuffers'
OL,7,FVerity Davidge, policy director at
OL,8,FMake UK, said: "Manufacturers feel
OL,9,Flike they are currently wading through
OL,10,Ftreacle, facing barriers and increased
OL,11,Fcosts being imposed on them at every
OL,12,Fturn.
OL,14,F"The one light at the end of the
OL,15,Ftunnel is the prospect of a modern,
OL,16,Flong-term industrial strategy which
OL,17,Fwill enable them to plan for the
OL,18,Ffuture with confidence in a supportive
OL,19,Fpolicy environment.
